Package com.github.choonchernlim.betterPreconditions.exception

Exception Summary
BooleanFalsePreconditionException This exception is thrown if the value is not true.
BooleanTruePreconditionException This exception is thrown if the value is true.
CollectionEmptyPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the collection is not empty.
CollectionNotEmptyPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the collection is empty.
JodaTimeEqualPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the first value is equal to second value.
JodaTimeNotEqualPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the first value is not equal to second value.
ObjectNotNullPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the value is not null.
ObjectNullPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the value is not null.
PreconditionException Abstract class for all precondition exceptions.
StringBlankPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the value is not blank.
StringNotBlankPreconditionException This exception is thrown if the value is blank.
